headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Podium Vehicle: Itali RSX
content: Stop by the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort to spin the Lucky Wheel and walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, mystery items, and more. This week's top prize on the podium is the Itali RSX - a luxury sportscar that elicits all sorts of reactions, including (but not limited to): envious whistles, expletives, and nervous yelps: all are appropriate.
